sequenceDiagram
    actor U as 用户
    participant C as Coordinator
    participant TD as TaskDecomposer
    participant OC as OpenClawAdapter
    participant OCG as OpenClaw Gateway<br/>ws://127.0.0.1:18679
    participant CL as ClaudeAdapter
    participant CLA as Claude API<br/>anthropic.com/v1/messages
    participant HM as HermesAdapter
    participant HMB as Hermes ACP Broker<br/>tcp://127.0.0.1:9001
    participant RM as ResultMerger

    U->>C: "帮我写一篇关于量子计算的论文"
    C->>TD: decompose(request)
    TD->>C: SubTask[] + Plan (3 stages, sequential)

    Note over C: === STAGE 1: Research ===
    C->>OC: task_request(sub-1, researcher)
    OC->>OCG: WebSocket req<br/>fn=sessions_spawn, model=kimi-latest
    Note right of OCG: 模拟延迟 1200ms
    OCG->>OC: WebSocket res<br/>status=ok, result=研究资料
    OC->>C: task_result(研究资料, score=0.91)

    Note over C: === STAGE 2: Draft ===
    C->>CL: task_request(sub-2, writer)<br/>deps={sub-1}
    CL->>CLA: HTTP POST<br/>model=claude-3-opus, max_tokens=4096
    Note right of CLA: 模拟延迟 2500ms
    CLA->>CL: HTTP 200 + SSE<br/>content=完整论文
    CL->>C: task_result(论文草稿, score=0.93)

    Note over C: === STAGE 3: Review ===
    C->>HM: task_request(sub-3, reviewer)<br/>deps={sub-2}
    HM->>HMB: ACP TASK_ASSIGN<br/>version=acp/2.1
    Note right of HMB: 模拟延迟 1800ms
    HMB->>HM: ACP TASK_RESULT<br/>verdict=APPROVED_WITH_REVISIONS
    HM->>C: task_result(审查意见, score=0.87)

    Note over C: === MERGE ===
    C->>RM: merge(strategy=sequential_append)
    RM->>C: mergedOutput + finalScore=90.3%

    C->>U: 完整论文 + 审查意见
